{"tid":427541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"左眼腫晒仍反勝河野公平 星如苦戰22連勝","createTime":"2017-10-07T14:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T15:15:54.000Z","uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b01ad3516bf4e6750797255e24835869e71ed815","tid":427541,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"香港拳王曹星如今晚在灣仔會展舉行的王者對決3，與36歲日本前世界冠軍河野公平，角逐WBO超蠅級國際冠軍賽，結果30歲的星如不負全場爆滿的八千觀眾厚望，在12回合賽事中戰至第六回合，證拳因星如眼部傷勢不能比賽，但仍判他以點數擊敗對手，職業生涯保持22場全勝的不敗戰績。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20171007/57302404?_ga=2.146684916.1174149014.1507386869-2103395644.1463026454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20171007%2F57302404%3F_ga%3D2.146684916.1174149014.1507386869-2103395644.1463026454&d=7odb22hZEKAF87K0rWuuPP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c9d7008c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20171007%2F57302404%3F_ga%3D2.146684916.1174149014.1507386869-2103395644.1463026454&h=37bcc959\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20171007/57302404?_ga=2.146684916.1174149014.1507386869-2103395644.1463026454</a>"},{"pid":"f583dfacc6357977818fac9277d97d0c478e4896","tid":427541,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd81da7c52711d470bfcc0bd4b009880561b11b5","tid":427541,"uid":147225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"咁網球選手受傷退賽係咪可以計返之前嗰啲局數比分決定勝負"},{"pid":"04c6b501b49f2158134908025315345e788534a3","tid":427541,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"當當正正打多場啦"},{"pid":"f209bf009fd53f8be2b7f45aa363f9b8c718056e","tid":427541,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:41:53.000Z","m